"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A woman who breast-feeds an infant.</p>\n<h2>The child's mother as nurse</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:7\">GEN 21:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:21\">1KI 3:21</a></p>\n<h2>A servant as nurse</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:7\">EXO 2:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:9\">EXO 2:9</a></p>\n<h3>Often wet-nurses remained in the family after the child was weaned</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:56-Gen24:59\">GEN 24:56–24:59</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:8\">GEN 35:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam4:4\">2SA 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs11:2-2Kgs11:3\">2KI 11:2–11:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr22:11\">2CH 22:11</a></p>\n<h2>Metaphorical use</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:12\">NUM 11:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:9-Isa66:13\">ISA 66:9–66:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:3\">LAM 4:3</a></p>",
